{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Track Conversation Progress",
  "description": "Monitors conversation history and automatically updates project_status.md with implementation progress, next steps, and detailed debug logs whenever the conversation evolves",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileEdited",
    "patterns": [
      ".claude/**/*",
      "src/**/*",
      "electron/**/*",
      "docs/**/*",
      "*.md",
      "*.json",
      "*.ts",
      "*.tsx"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Review the entire conversation history and all recent file changes. Update the project_status.md file with:\n\n1. **What Has Been Implemented**: List all completed features, fixes, and changes discussed in this conversation with timestamps and file references\n2. **What's Next**: Prioritized list of upcoming tasks, features, or issues to address based on the conversation\n3. **Detailed Debug Log**: Comprehensive log including:\n   - Conversation milestones and decisions made\n   - Code changes and their rationale\n   - Issues encountered and resolutions\n   - Agent invocations and their outcomes\n   - File modifications with context\n   - Performance considerations\n   - Security reviews performed\n   - Testing status\n   - Technical debt identified\n\nFormat the update clearly with sections, timestamps, and actionable items. Maintain historical context while highlighting recent progress."
  }
}